OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMicrosoft to pay $20m for  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchild privacy violations   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Microsoft will pay $20m (#16m) to US   
OL,6, federal regulators after it was found  
OL,7, to have illegally collected data on    
OL,8, children who had started Xbox accounts.
OL,10,FThe Federal Trade Commission (FTC)     
OL,11,Freached a settlement with the company  
OL,12,Fon Monday, which also includes         
OL,13,Fincreased protections for child gamers.
OL,15,FAmong other violations, the FTC found  
OL,16,Fthat Microsoft failed to inform parents
OL,17,Fabout its data collection policies.    
OL,19,FIt follows a similar action against    
OL,20,FAmazon last week over its Echo devices.
